  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2110",
  "title": "Remove docs build from Travis",
  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\n\r\nboth I guess\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the current behavior?**\r\n\r\nTravis installs and runs the docs\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the expected behavior?**\r\n\r\nTravis doesn’t care about the docs \r\n\r\n**Feature: What is your use case for such a feature?**\r\n\r\nHave faster builds\r\n\r\n**Feature: What is your proposed API entry? The new option to add? What is the behavior?**\r\n\r\nRely on Netlify for the build status of the docs\r\n\r\n\r\nSee also https://github.com/algolia/react-instantsearch/issues/33.\r\n\r\nThis can be done when we move towards the new docs in v2, since the docs don’t run yet :) ",
